PART 2: TECHNICAL FOUNDATION
============================

PYTHON'S ROLE IN AI DEVELOPMENT
================================

Why Python for AI?
-----------------
• Large developer community
• Extensive pre-built frameworks
• Research primarily done in Python
• Reduces development time significantly
• Easy to learn and use

Popular AI Frameworks in Python:
-------------------------------
• TensorFlow (Google)
• PyTorch (Meta)
• Scikit-learn
• Hugging Face Transformers
• LangChain
• OpenAI API

Important Clarification:
-----------------------
Python ≠ Generative AI
Python = Programming Language (Tool)
Generative AI = Field of Study (Domain)

